        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[cpan.org email forwarding has been shut down ]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[The Perl NOC team has shut down the forwarding of email to the cpan addresses. If you are a CPAN author, please make sure MetaCPAN displays ways to contact you. (link to the source git repository of your projects, a LinkedIn account, an email address, etc.)]]></description>
